1. Ona je nosila halj*inu sa uzorkom cveća. (She was wearing a dress with a flower pattern.)
2. Halj*ina joj je bila u beloj boji. (Her dress was in white color.)
3. On je kupio halj*inu za njen rođendan. (He bought a dress for her birthday.)
4. Ona je halj*inu obukla uz crvene čizme. (She wore the dress with red boots.)
5. Ona je izabrala halj*inu sa dugim rukavima. (She chose a dress with long sleeves.)